# Pre-commit gate. Two checks, in order, fail-fast:
#   1. tsc — catch type errors before they hit the diff. Cheap
#      on an incremental run, prevents "fix the type error in CI"
#      churn.
#   2. vitest — run the unit-test suite. Currently fast (<5s).
#
# Bypass with `git commit --no-verify` only when committing
# something genuinely unfinishable in this checkout (work-in-
# progress branches before a final cleanup commit). Don't make
# it a habit.
npm run precommit
